                    &connectionFactoryAdvancedResourceConfigProps;

                    
                        Whether on not to use local transactions - default is false.
                    
                    
                    
                        Whether the connection should be locked into the transaction.
                    

                    
                        Whether on not to use XA transactions - default is false.
                    

                    
                        Maximum time in minutes an XA Resource can be idle before it is removed.
